*.pyc

# Regenerable caches -- tokenized corpus tensors, Ducky SDK setup (graph +
# calibration), rebuilt automatically from source data/tokenizer when
# missing. Not source of truth, and some exceed GitHub's 100MB file limit.
data/cache/

# Regenerable corpus builds -- rebuilt by extract_code_corpus.py (from the
# local stdlib + curated site-packages libraries) and
# extract_gutenberg_corpus.py (from Project Gutenberg) respectively. Not
# source of truth, and both now exceed or approach GitHub's 100MB limit as
# the corpora have grown -- the extraction scripts are the source of truth,
# these are their output.
data/code/corpus.txt
data/code/pairs.jsonl
data/text/gutenberg_corpus.txt
data/text/_pg_catalog_cache.csv
